t\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-3-1-2\" data-name=\"testimonial quote text\">\"Mechanics Shiva and Deepak are highly skilled and provide excellent service. However, I felt the spare parts were priced slightly higher than expected.\"</p>\n<span class=\"text-[10px] font-black uppercase text-white/40 mt-4 block\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-3-1-3\" data-name=\"testimonial author name\">Roshan Anand</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"absolute top-[35%] left-[2%] z-30 rotate-[3deg] scattered-card\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-4\" data-name=\"mid left testimonial card container\" data-scroll=\"\" data-scroll-speed=\"-0.1\">\n<div class=\"bg-[var(--k-color-bg-surface)] p-8 brutalist-border shadow-[8px_8px_0_var(--k-color-accent)] max-w-[300px]\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-4-1\" data-name=\"mid left testimonial card\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3 text-[var(--k-color-accent)]\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-4-1-1\" data-name=\"testimonial card label wrapper\"><i class=\"ti ti-bolt\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-4-1-1-1\" data-name=\"bolt icon\"></i><span class=\"text-[9px] font-black uppercase\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-4-1-1-2\" data-name=\"label text\">OLA EXPERT</span></div>\n<p class=\"text-base text-white review-text\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-4-1-2\" data-name=\"testimonial quote text\">\"Excellent Ola repair centre. They successfully resolved my electric charging system issue.\"</p>\n<span class=\"text-[10px] font-black uppercase text-white/40 mt-4 block\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-4-1-3\" data-name=\"testimonial author name\">Paresh Jani</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"absolute top-[40%] right-[2%] z-30 rotate-[-5deg] scattered-card\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-5\" data-name=\"mid right testimonial card container\" data-scroll=\"\" data-scroll-speed=\"0.12\">\n<div class=\"bg-[var(--k-color-bg-surface)] p-8 brutalist-border shadow-[12px_12px_0_white] max-w-[320px]\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-5-1\" data-name=\"mid right testimonial card\">\n<p class=\"text-base text-white review-text\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-5-1-1\" data-name=\"testimonial quote text\">\"Excellent shop for repairs and auto parts. They offer quality products, quick service, and complete customer satisfaction.\"</p>\n<span class=\"text-[10px] font-black uppercase text-white/40 mt-4 block\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-5-1-2\" data-name=\"testimonial author name\">Mahendra Sunar</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"absolute bottom-[20%] left-[5%] z-20 rotate-[-4deg] scattered-card\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-6\" data-name=\"bottom left testimonial card container\" data-scroll=\"\" data-scroll-speed=\"0.1\">\n<div class=\"bg-[var(--k-color-bg-surface)] p-8 brutalist-border border-l-4 border-l-[var(--k-color-accent)] max-w-[350px]\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-6-1\" data-name=\"bottom left testimonial card\">\n<p class=\"text-base text-white review-text\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-6-1-1\" data-name=\"testimonial quote text\">\"My Ola scooter was repaired perfectly. Very satisfied with the service.\"</p>\n<span class=\"text-[10px] font-black uppercase text-white/40 mt-4 block\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-6-1-2\" data-name=\"testimonial author name\">Rajesh Kumar Gupta</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"absolute bottom-[25%] right-[5%] z-20 rotate-[6deg] scattered-card\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-7\" data-name=\"bottom right testimonial card container\" data-scroll=\"\" data-scroll-speed=\"0.18\">\n<div class=\"bg-[var(--k-color-bg-surface)] p-8 brutalist-border shadow-[12px_12px_0_var(--k-color-accent)] max-w-[300px]\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-7-1\" data-name=\"bottom right testimonial card\">\n<p class=\"text-base text-white review-text\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-7-1-1\" data-name=\"testimonial quote text\">\"Excellent service. Batteries and tyres are readily available, and the repair work is outstanding.\"</p>\n<span class=\"text-[10px] font-black uppercase text-white/40 mt-4 block\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-7-1-2\" data-name=\"testimonial author name\">Sonu Sharma</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"absolute bottom-[5%] left-[25%] z-20 rotate-[-2deg] scattered-card\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-8\" data-name=\"bottom center testimonial card container\" data-scroll=\"\" data-scroll-speed=\"0.05\">\n<div class=\"bg-[var(--k-color-bg-surface)] p-6 brutalist-border border-t-4 border-t-white/20 max-w-[280px]\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-8-1\" data-name=\"bottom center testimonial card\">\n<p class=\"text-sm text-white/60 italic review-text\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-8-1-1\" data-name=\"testimonial quote text\">\"Very good service at affordable rates. Great value for money.\"</p>\n<span class=\"text-[10px] font-black uppercase text-white/40 mt-3 block\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-8-1-2\" data-name=\"testimonial author name\">Neeha Chauhan</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"absolute top-[20%] right-[30%] z-10 rotate-[12deg] opacity-40 scale-75\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-9\" data-name=\"extra quick review container\">\n<div class=\"bg-white/5 p-4 brutalist-border max-w-[200px]\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-9-1\" data-name=\"extra quick review card\">\n<p class=\"text-[10px] text-white\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-9-1-1\" data-name=\"testimonial quote text\">\"Very fast service with experienced mechanics.\"</p>\n<span class=\"text-[8px] font-black uppercase text-[var(--k-color-accent)]\" data-kid=\"8-1-2-9-1-2\" data-name=\"testimonial author name\">Raju Raza</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<footer class=\"py-20 md:py-32 px-6 md:px-8 border-t border-white/5 bg-black\" data-kid=\"9\">\n<div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-12 text-center lg:text-left\" data-kid=\"9-1\">\n<div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-6\" data-kid=\"9-1-1\">\n<img alt=\"Logo\" class=\"h-16 w-auto\" data-kid=\"9-1-1-1\" src=\"/api/local/images/.kombai/krishna-logo-new.png\">\n<p class=\"text-[10px] font-black text-white/20 uppercase tracking-[0.3em]\" data-kid=\"9-1-1-2\">Krishna Automobiles Mira Road East. Since 2009.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex gap-6\" data-kid=\"9-1-2\">\n<a class=\"w-16 h-16 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-[var(--k-color-accent)] transition-all\" data-kid=\"9-1-2-1\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"ti ti-phone-filled text-2xl text-white\" data-kid=\"9-1-2-1-1\"></i></a>\n<a class=\"w-16 h-16 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-[#25D366] transition-all\" data-kid=\"9-1-2-2\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-whatsapp text-3xl text-white\" data-kid=\"9-1-2-2-1\"></i></a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</footer>\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3/dist/gsap.min.js\" data-kid=\"10\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3/dist/ScrollTrigger.min.js\" data-kid=\"11\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/locomotive-scroll@5/bundled/locomotive-scroll.min.js\" data-kid=\"12\"></script>\n<script type=\"module\" data-kid=\"13\">\n    import Lenis from \"https://esm.sh/lenis@1\";\n    const lenis = new Lenis({ autoRaf: true });\n    const locomotiveScroll = new LocomotiveScroll();\n    gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);\n\n    const dock = document.getElementById('magnetic-dock-container');\n    gsap.to(dock, {\n        y: 0, opacity: 1, ease: \"power3.out\",\n        scrollTrigger: { trigger: \"body\", start: \"100px top\", scrub: 1 }\n    });\n</script>",
