description text\">Status: active // 09:00 - 21:30</span>\n</div>\n<p class=\"text-[var(--secondary-gray)] text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-md\" data-kid=\"1-3-1-3-2-2\">\n            Authorized multi-brand component handling. Industrial-grade charging. Precision carburetor calibration. Sonic remediation protocols applied to all performance fuel systems.\n          </p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"absolute -bottom-10 -right-20 font-display text-[25vw] font-black opacity-[0.02] select-none pointer-events-none whitespace-nowrap parallax-watermark\" data-kid=\"1-3-2\">\n      PROTOCOLS\n    </div>\n</header>\n\n<div class=\"ticker-wrap relative z-10\" data-kid=\"1-4\">\n<div class=\"ticker-content flex items-center gap-24 font-mono text-xs uppercase font-bold tracking-[0.2em]\" data-kid=\"1-4-1\">\n<span class=\"text-white\" data-kid=\"1-4-1-1\">Battery Service <span class=\"text-[var(--accent-red)]\" data-kid=\"1-4-1-1-1\">₹150</span></span>\n<span class=\"text-white\" data-kid=\"1-4-1-2\">Brake Service <span class=\"text-[var(--accent-red)]\" data-kid=\"1-4-1-2-1\">₹200</span></span>\n<span class=\"text-white\" data-kid=\"1-4-1-3\">Carburetor Cleaning <span class=\"text-[var(--accent-red)]\" data-kid=\"1-4-1-3-1\">₹450</span></span>\n<span class=\"text-white\" data-kid=\"1-4-1-4\">Vehicle Delivery <span class=\"text-[var(--accent-red)]\" data-kid=\"1-4-1-4-1\">₹100</span></span>\n<span class=\"text-white\" data-kid=\"1-4-1-5\">Oil Change <span class=\"text-[var(--accent-red)]\" data-kid=\"1-4-1-5-1\">Special Offer</span></span>\n<span class=\"text-white\" data-kid=\"1-4-1-6\">Engine Overhaul <span class=\"text-[var(--accent-red)]\" data-kid=\"1-4-1-6-1\">From ₹2500</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"text-white\" data-kid=\"1-4-1-7\">Battery Service <span class=\"text-[var(--accent-red)]\" data-kid=\"1-4-1-7-1\">₹150</span></span>\n<span class=\"text-white\" data-kid=\"1-4-1-8\">Brake Service <span class=\"text-[var(--accent-red)]\" data-kid=\"1-4-1-8-1\">₹200</s