ame=\"spare stock count 2\">STK: 86</span>\n</div>\n<h4 class=\"text-lg font-black uppercase tracking-[0.1em] leading-tight mb-8\" data-kid=\"1-7-2-3-2\">Studds <br data-kid=\"1-7-2-3-2-1\">Helmets</h4>\n<div class=\"mt-auto border-t border-white/5 pt-4\" data-kid=\"1-7-2-3-3\" data-name=\"spare footer 2\">\n<span class=\"technical-label text-[8px] text-[var(--secondary-gray)]\" data-kid=\"1-7-2-3-3-1\" data-name=\"spare status 2\">Certified Safety Gear</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"spare-card group industrial-corner lg:col-span-1\" data-kid=\"1-7-2-4\">\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-4\" data-kid=\"1-7-2-4-1\">\n<span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-[var(--accent-red)]\" data-kid=\"1-7-2-4-1-1\" data-name=\"spare ID 3\">INV-03</span>\n<span class=\"text-[8px] font-bold text-[var(--secondary-gray)] opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-100\" data-kid=\"1-7-2-4-1-2\" data-name=\"spare stock count 3\">STK: 210</span>\n</div>\n<h4 class=\"text-lg font-black uppercase tracking-[0.1em] leading-tight mb-8\" data-kid=\"1-7-2-4-2\">Castrol <br data-kid=\"1-7-2-4-2-1\">Lubricants</h4>\n<div class=\"mt-auto border-t border-white/5 pt-4\" data-kid=\"1-7-2-4-3\" data-name=\"spare footer 3\">\n<span class=\"technical-label text-[8px] text-[var(--secondary-gray)]\" data-kid=\"1-7-2-4-3-1\" data-name=\"spare status 3\">High-Performance Fluids</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"spare-card group industrial-corner lg:col-span-1\" data-kid=\"1-7-2-5\">\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-4\" data-kid=\"1-7-2-5-1\">\n<span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-[var(--accent-red)]\" data-kid=\"1-7-2-5-1-1\" data-name=\"spare ID 4\">INV-04</span>\n<span class=\"text-[8px] font-bold text-[var(--secondary-gray)] opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-100\" data-kid=\"1-7-2-5-1-2\" data-name=\"spare stock count 4\">STK: 45</span>\n</div>\n<h4 class=\"text-lg font-black uppercase tracking-[0.1em] leading-tight mb-8\" data-kid=\"1-7-2-5-2\">BS6 <br data-kid=\"1-7-2-5-2-1\">Specials</h4>\n<div class=\"mt-auto border-t border-white/5 pt-4\" data-kid=\"1-7-2-5-3\" data-name=\"spare footer 4\">\n<span class=\"technical-label text-[8px] text-[var(--secondary-gray)]\" data-kid=\"1-7-2-5-3-1\" data-name=\"spare status 4\">Electronic Fuel Components</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n<footer class=\"bg-[var(--surface)] border-t border-[var(--border-dark)] pt-32 pb-20 px-10 md:px-24\" data-kid=\"1-8\">\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-20 mb-32\" data-kid=\"1-8-1\">\n<div class=\"col-span-1 md:col-span-1\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-1\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-10\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-1-1\">\n<div class=\"w-10 h-10 bg-[var(--accent-red)] flex items-center justify-center font-bold italic text-white rounded-xs\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-1-1-1\">K</div>\n<span class=\"font-bold tracking-tighter text-2xl uppercase\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-1-1-2\">Krishna <br data-kid=\"1-8-1-1-1-2-1\"><span class=\"text-[var(--accent-red)] text-lg\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-1-1-2-2\">Automobile</span></span>\n</div>\n<p class=\"text-[var(--secondary-gray)] text-xs uppercase tracking-widest leading-loose mb-10\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-1-2\">\n          Mumbai's surgical mechanical center since 2009. Precision for the ride.\n        </p>\n<div class=\"flex gap-4\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-1-3\">\n<a class=\"w-12 h-12 border border-[var(--border-dark)] flex items-center justify-center rounded-full hover:border-[var(--accent-red)] hover:text-[var(--accent-red)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-1-3-1\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fa-brands fa-whatsapp\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-1-3-1-1\"></i></a>\n<a class=\"w-12 h-12 border border-[var(--border-dark)] flex items-center justify-center rounded-full hover:border-[var(--accent-red)] hover:text-[var(--accent-red)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-1-3-2\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fa-brands fa-instagram\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-1-3-2-1\"></i></a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div data-kid=\"1-8-1-2\">\n<h4 class=\"technical-label text-white mb-8\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-2-1\">Service Protocols</h4>\n<ul class=\"space-y-4 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[var(--secondary-gray)]\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-2-2\">\n<li data-kid=\"1-8-1-2-2-1\"><a class=\"hover:text-[var(--accent-red)]\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-2-2-1-1\" href=\"#\">Engine Diagnostics</a></li>\n<li data-kid=\"1-8-1-2-2-2\"><a class=\"hover:text-[var(--accent-red)]\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-2-2-2-1\" href=\"#\">Electrical Schematics</a></li>\n<li data-kid=\"1-8-1-2-2-3\"><a class=\"hover:text-[var(--accent-red)]\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-2-2-3-1\" href=\"#\">Brake Calibration</a></li>\n<li data-kid=\"1-8-1-2-2-4\"><a class=\"hover:text-[var(--accent-red)]\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-2-2-4-1\" href=\"#\">Inventory Logistics</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div data-kid=\"1-8-1-3\">\n<h4 class=\"technical-label text-white mb-8\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-3-1\">Operations</h4>\n<div class=\"space-y-6 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[var(--secondary-gray)]\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-3-2\">\n<div class=\"flex justify-between border-b border-[var(--border-dark)] pb-4\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-3-2-1\">\n<span data-kid=\"1-8-1-3-2-1-1\">Daily</span>\n<span class=\"text-white\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-3-2-1-2\">09:00 - 21:30</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex justify-between border-b border-[var(--border-dark)] pb-4\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-3-2-2\">\n<span data-kid=\"1-8-1-3-2-2-1\">Status</span>\n<span class=\"text-[var(--accent-red)]\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-3-2-2-2\">LIVE // OPEN</span>\n</div>\n<p class=\"leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-3-2-3\">Shop No.11, Gaurav Sankalp Chintan 11, Hatkesh, Mira Road East, 401107</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div data-kid=\"1-8-1-4\">\n<h4 class=\"technical-label text-white mb-8\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-4-1\">Connectivity</h4>\n<div class=\"space-y-6 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[var(--secondary-gray)]\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-4-2\">\n<a class=\"block text-xl text-white hover:text-[var(--accent-red)] transition-colors tracking-tighter\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-4-2-1\" href=\"tel:09322245569\">093222 45569</a>\n<a class=\"block text-xl text-white hover:text-[var(--accent-red)] transition-colors tracking-tighter\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-4-2-2\" href=\"tel:09082744210\">090827 44210</a>\n<div class=\"pt-4\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-4-2-3\">\n<button class=\"w-full border-2 border-[var(--accent-red)] text-[var(--accent-red)] py-4 hover:bg-[var(--accent-red)] hover:text-white transition-all uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px]\" data-kid=\"1-8-1-4-2-3-1\">Instant Recall</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center pt-10 border-t border-[var(--border-dark)] technical-label text-[var(--secondary-gray)] opacity-50\" data-kid=\"1-8-2\">\n<p data-kid=\"1-8-2-1\">© 2024 KRISHNA AUTOMOBILE. ALL PROTOCOLS ENFORCED.</p>\n<div class=\"flex gap-10 mt-6 md:mt-0\" data-kid=\"1-8-2-2\">\n<span data-kid=\"1-8-2-2-1\">ISO 9001:2015 CERTIFIED</span>\n<span data-kid=\"1-8-2-2-2\">TECHNICAL EXCELLENCE</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</footer>\n</div>\n\n<link data-kid=\"2\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3/dist/gsap.min.js\" data-kid=\"4\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3/dist/ScrollTrigger.min.js\" data-kid=\"5\"></script>\n<link data-kid=\"3\" href=\"https://unpkg.com/lenis@1/dist/lenis.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n<script type=\"module\" data-kid=\"6\">\n  import Lenis from \"https://esm.sh/lenis@1\"\n  const lenis = new Lenis()\n  function raf(time) {\n    lenis.raf(time)\n    requestAnimationFrame(raf)\n  }\n  requestAnimationFrame(raf)\n</script>\n<script data-kid=\"7\">\n  gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);\n\n  window.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {\n    // Reveal Entrance\n    gsap.from('.reveal-up', {\n      y: 100,\n      opacity: 0,\n      duration: 1.2,\n      stagger: 0.2,\n      ease: \"expo.out\",\n      scrollTrigger: {\n        trigger: '.reveal-up',\n        start: 'top 85%'\n      }\n    });\n\n    // Stagger Items\n    gsap.from('.protocol-item', {\n      y: 60,\n      opacity: 0,\n      duration: 1,\n      stagger: 0.1,\n      ease: \"power3.out\",\n      scrollTrigger: {\n        trigger: '.protocol-grid',\n        start: 'top 80%'\n      }\n    });\n\n    // Stagger Catalog\n    gsap.from('.reveal-item', {\n      x: -20,\n      opacity: 0,\n      duration: 0.8,\n      stagger: 0.1,\n      ease: \"power2.out\",\n      scrollTrigger: {\n        trigger: '.reveal-stagger',\n        start: 'top 80%'\n      }\n    });\n\n    // Watermark Parallax\n    gsap.to('.parallax-watermark', {\n      xPercent: -20,\n      scrollTrigger: {\n        trigger: 'header',\n        scrub: true,\n        start: 'top top',\n        end: 'bottom top'\n      }\n    });\n\n    // Grid Background Movement\n    gsap.to('.grid-pattern', {\n      backgroundPosition: '0 1000px',\n      scrollTrigger: {\n        trigger: 'body',\n        scrub: 2,\n        start: 'top top',\n        end: 'bottom bottom'\n      }\n    });\n  });\n</script>\n",
